{"tid":2312523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中文維基百科禁止記載電視台記者名單","createTime":"2020-12-05T04:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T00:54:21.000Z","uid":10540,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d977ecf781af41f1a5ac369fa894a86fce74b2c4","tid":2312523,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jer9rWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJer9rWt.jpg&h=822f7c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼早前有線電視後，近日now新聞同CCTVB嘅成員名單亦被突然原始研究為由而被刪去，而有關名單存在10多年。<br />\n<br />\n有用戶即使加入合法的來源，但亦被回退，之後因為被提出刪除嘅人認為屬「破壞」而被封鎖。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">可以見到而家維基同民政事務署一樣，不斷用方針規則「搬龍門」同收緊，去限制大家編輯嘅空間。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB嘅編輯戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&amp;action=history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fw%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3D%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%26action%3Dhistory&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=3b71a2ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&amp;action=history</a><br />\n<br />\n有線嘅編輯戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&amp;action=history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fw%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%26action%3Dhistory&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=73340cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&amp;action=history</a><br />\n<br />\nNow 新閒<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Now%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&amp;action=history\" data-sr-url